Package: clovers
Title: Probabilistic Models of Customer Lifetime Value (LTV)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Williams",
           family = "Jon",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jon.williams@warnerbros.com")
Description: Analyze customer retention and lifetime value (LTV)
    for contractual, discrete-time businesses using Fader and
    Hardie's Shifted Beta-Geometric (sBG) probability model. See
    Fader (2000) <doi:10.1002/dir.20074>. The package provides functions
    for data preparation, parameter estimation, model checking,
    LTV estimation, and plotting.
License: Apache 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
